metadata.description:
WOOFies is the NFT for dog people.

Hosted on the Ethereum Blockchain, the 5,555 PFP genesis collection will be your access key to all future mints, utility and exclusive offers.

Inspired by vintage video games (the original metaverse) and pop culture, we want WOOFies to be fun, playful and freakin' amazing (just like dogs).

The collection is made of 5 distinct breeds with 100 possible traits - so there's a WOOFie for everyone.
metadata.name: WOOFies #1
